mmpp 0.6 (2017-09-29)
- a bug in k2d function is fixed. 

mmpp 0.5 (2015-09-20)
- Some wording issues are addressed.

mmpp 0.4 (2015-08-20)
- Typos and inconsistencies in references are corrected.

mmpp 0.3 (2015-07-21)
- splitMPP now supports sliding window splitting with overlapping.
- By specifying "MarkCenter", the marks are flexibly centered. This can be helpful when considering the relative distance from main shock of the earthquake.


mmpp 0.2 (2015-02-28)
- Minor typos and incorrect descriptions are fixed
- ieimetric now has two options, "spike-weighted" variant and "time-weighted" variant.
Previous version only supports "time-weighted" variant. In this version, "spike-weighted" variant is set to default because of its computational efficiency. 


mmpp 0.1 (2015-02-20)
-----------------------
FIRST DEVELOPMENTAL VERSION
* This is the first developmental version to be made public. 
* mmpp (metrics for marked point process) provides functions for calculating various similarity and distance metrics for marked point process.
